#### Library Cataloging and Classification

For those who insist on imposing order on the digital wild west, there's [library cataloging](/Library_catalog) and [classification](/Library_classification). The main topic, the one we’re ostensibly discussing, is, of course, [artificial intelligence](/Artificial_intelligence). It’s filed under the [Library of Congress](/Library_of_Congress_Classification) system as Q334–Q342. And for the more… globally inclined, the [Universal Decimal](/Universal_Decimal_Classification) system places it under 004.8. Numbers and letters, trying to pin down something that’s still figuring out its own definition. Quaint.

